// Function to simulate API delay
export const simulateApiDelay = (ms = 1000) =>
    new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, ms));

// Function to simulate search with mock data
export const mockSearch = async (query) => {
    await simulateApiDelay(800); // Simulate network delay

    if (!query || query.length < 2) {
        return [];
    }

    const searchQuery = query.toLowerCase();

    return mockInventoryData
        .filter(item => {
            const modelNumber = (item.Model_Number || '').toLowerCase();
            const description = (item.Description || '').toLowerCase();
            const brand = (item.Brand || '').toLowerCase();

            return (
                modelNumber.includes(searchQuery) ||
                description.includes(searchQuery) ||
                brand.includes(searchQuery) ||
                modelNumber.startsWith(searchQuery)
            );
        })
        .sort((a, b) => {
            // Prioritize exact matches and prefix matches
            const aModel = (a.Model_Number || '').toLowerCase();
            const bModel = (b.Model_Number || '').toLowerCase();

            const aExact = aModel === searchQuery;
            const bExact = bModel === searchQuery;
            if (aExact && !bExact) return -1;
            if (!aExact && bExact) return 1;

            const aStartsWith = aModel.startsWith(searchQuery);
            const bStartsWith = bModel.startsWith(searchQuery);
            if (aStartsWith && !bStartsWith) return -1;
            if (!aStartsWith && bStartsWith) return 1;

            return aModel.localeCompare(bModel);
        })
        .slice(0, 50); // Limit results for performance
};
